  <brief_title>A Comparison of Three Treatments for Advanced HIV Disease in Patients Who Have Received Nucleoside Therapy in the Past</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Three-Arm Study Comparing Combination to Monthly Alternating Nucleoside Therapy for the Treatment of Advanced HIV Disease (CD4 &lt;= 50/mm3) With a Prior History of Nucleoside Therapy</official_title>
